Tylwica-Majątek is a &lt;a href="village"&gt;village&lt;/a&gt; in the administrative district of &lt;a href="Gmina%20Micha%C5%82owo"&gt;Gmina Michałowo&lt;/a&gt;, within &lt;a href="Bia%C5%82ystok%20County"&gt;Białystok County&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="Podlaskie%20Voivodeship"&gt;Podlaskie Voivodeship&lt;/a&gt;, in north-eastern &lt;a href="Poland"&gt;Poland&lt;/a&gt;, close to the border with &lt;a href="Belarus"&gt;Belarus&lt;/a&gt;. It lies approximately west of &lt;a href="Micha%C5%82owo"&gt;Michałowo&lt;/a&gt; and south-east of the regional capital &lt;a href="Bia%C5%82ystok"&gt;Białystok&lt;/a&gt;.
